{
  "chapter": 92,
  "chapter_summary": "寇仲与曲傲第三门徒庚哥呼儿及铁勒高手激战于高台附近，以井中月硬撼庚哥呼儿的\"狂浪七转\"剑法。徐子陵趁机登上高台，击碎木柱救下被缚的黄衣女子。二人携黄衣女子逃离至小山丘，发现她虽被点穴却无法唤醒，徐子陵为她通经活络后脸色泛青，疑有不妥。寇仲辨认出围攻者为曲傲手下庚哥呼儿及独霸山庄的人。二人对黄衣女子诡异的美貌既惊艳又警惕，怀疑她可能是阴癸派与师妃暄决斗的嫡传弟子，这一切或许是为引他们入局而设的陷阱。饥饿狼群逼近时，二人不忍弃她于不顾，用树枝扎成担架将其抬走。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "真奇怪，她该是给点了穴道，但无论我怎样为她通经活络，她仍是昏迷不醒。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 109,
      "line_end": 111
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "倾国倾城之美大概就是这样子，难怪两帮人马要为她打生打死。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 117,
      "line_end": 119
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "只看她乌黑的发质，雪白的肌肤，便如天生丽质该作何解。我从未见过这么漂亮诱人的秀发冰肌，美丽得近乎诡异。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 121,
      "line_end": 125
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "你说得对，本来见美女总会心热，为何刚才我却是心生寒意呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 127,
      "line_end": 129
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "她会否根本不是人呢？横看竖看她都像精灵多过像人，人那有这么美丽呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 133,
      "line_end": 135
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你好像忘了原先蹲下来看她的原因哩！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 137,
      "line_end": 137
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "因她美得太惊心动魄了。咦！为何你的脸色这么难看？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 139,
      "line_end": 141
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "或者是因为我刚才想为她打通穴道时用了太多真力吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 143,
      "line_end": 145
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "该是这个原因了！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 147,
      "line_end": 147
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "我去瞧瞧有没有敌人追来，你在这看看有没有办法弄醒她吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 149,
      "line_end": 151
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "还是一起去看为佳！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 153,
      "line_end": 153
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "非常不妥，以前就算在你力战之后，脸色也不会白中泛青，现在经我输入真气后，你这青色才退去。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 157,
      "line_end": 159
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "这女人不但美得邪门，人也邪门得很，看来我是了她道儿。天下间那有我们解不开的封穴的手法呢？难道点她穴道的强得过跋锋寒吗？这是不可能的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 161,
      "line_end": 165
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "若点她穴道的是曲傲又如何呢？别忘记曲傲的功力只是差毕玄少许？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 167,
      "line_end": 169
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你碰到曲傲吗？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 171,
      "line_end": 171
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "若碰上曲傲，还有命儿在这和你研究是否救了个妖女回来吗？唉！这么美的妖女，竟使我觉得即使被她害死都是心甘情愿。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 173,
      "line_end": 177
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "刚才那批人是曲傲的手下，那使剑使得不错的自称是曲傲的三徒儿庚哥呼儿。另一边的人则是独霸山庄，只听名字便知也不是什么好人了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 179,
      "line_end": 183
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "他们为甚么会为这妖女打起来呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 185,
      "line_end": 185
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "见到她那诡异的美丽，我便有胆颤心惊的感觉，红颜祸水怕就是这级数的动人尤物。告诉我，你曾想像过有人竟可比单琬晶、沈落雁、李秀宁她们更美吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 187,
      "line_end": 191
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "我们唯一的选择，确是走为上着。咦！为何你愈走愈慢了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 193,
      "line_end": 195
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "小陵啊！你教教我吧！假若我们真是好人作贼办，人家姑娘确是清清白白的，却给我们疑神疑鬼的害得给铁勒人擒回去，又或被野兽吃掉，我们的良心会安乐吗？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 197,
      "line_end": 199
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "但怎样解释我脸上会现青气呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 201,
      "line_end": 203
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "在救起她之前，你有否和甚么特别厉害的人交过手？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 205,
      "line_end": 205
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "确是碰上个使双刃的铁勒美女，但她尚未有资格伤我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 207,
      "line_end": 209
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "曲傲的武功古古怪怪的，像那庚哥呼儿便能以一种奇怪的方法增强力道，或者那铁勒美人儿暗中伤了你都说不定，所以错怪她为妖女的可能应是存在的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 211,
      "line_end": 213
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "她或是个丝毫不懂武功的弱质女子，否则便是武功高明得连我们都察觉不到她体内的怪异真气。唉！我也不知该怎样处理她了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 215,
      "line_end": 217
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "照道理这该不会是个为我们而设的陷阱，因为她怎知我们会去救她呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 219,
      "line_end": 221
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "但为何我们总有不妥当的感觉？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 223,
      "line_end": 223
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "回去看看再说吧。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 225,
      "line_end": 225
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "看她的模样儿，绝不该超过二十岁，就算她的师傅是毕玄或傅采林，也难使她的功力足以深藏不露至可瞒过我们的地步。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 235,
      "line_end": 237
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "若她是另一个似师妃暄……天……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 239,
      "line_end": 239
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "我的奶奶！若她是阴癸派那要与师妃暄决斗的嫡传弟子，这一切都变成有可能了。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 243,
      "line_end": 245
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "这个可能性太大了。任少名是曲傲的儿子，恶僧艳尼则是阴癸派的人，否则为何会缚她在柱子上一副等我们去救的样子。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 247,
      "line_end": 249
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "定是这样。走吧！看她能躺到何时？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 251,
      "line_end": 251
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "回去再说吧！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 267,
      "line_end": 267
    }
  ],
